=short

<p>Many definitions are conditional: their existence can be limited
based on very flexible expressions.</p>

=schema

==xml
<attributeGroup name="selector">
  <attribute name="when"   type="ms:Expression" />
  <attribute name="unless" type="ms:Expression" />
</attributeGroup>
==end

=description

<p><a href="/explain/base/expressions.html">Learn about expressions</a>.
Use either <code>ms:when</codett> or <code>ms:unless</code>, or neither.</p>
